30:44.416 --> 30:45.666
Again. Go!

30:45.750 --> 30:48.166
Go again. Harder, don't stop. Hit.

30:48.250 --> 30:51.583
Go, go, hit! Harder!
Use the other one too!

30:51.666 --> 30:53.625
Come on, get it out! Get it out, huh?

30:53.708 --> 30:57.625
Way to go! Enough, enough, enough.
