32:46.250 --> 32:48.375
Mmm. Mm-hmm.

32:49.625 --> 32:53.125
Mm, no, no, no, no.
Come on, we did that last time.

32:54.791 --> 32:56.041
Mmm.

32:56.125 --> 32:59.291
