34:09.083 --> 34:12.166
You really are a pig.

34:12.250 --> 34:13.541
You know that?

34:13.625 --> 34:16.333
Yeah, I'm a piggy too.

34:16.416 --> 34:18.125
A real pig.

34:18.208 --> 34:19.958
