35:34.958 --> 35:37.541
He worked with his brother,
but nobody knows what happened to him.

35:37.625 --> 35:40.500
-Take me to where this asshole lives.
-I've already checked the place out.

35:40.583 --> 35:43.083
The property's barred up.
Plus, the van ain't there anymore.

35:43.166 --> 35:45.041
