and you don't use it.

36:48.458 --> 36:50.375
You don't even wanna fix it.

36:50.458 --> 36:52.583
And you don't have the balls
to speak with your father.

36:52.666 --> 36:55.791
If I had more time,
I'd fix you as well. Ha!

36:55.875 --> 36:57.708
Depressed artist, come and see this.

37:00.916 --> 37:02.416
Jack, that's awesome.

37:06.250 --> 37:07.666
Who the fuck is that?

37:19.083 --> 37:19.916
