37:20.000 --> 37:22.500
Water department.
There's a leak in the area.

37:31.541 --> 37:32.916
-Hello.
-Hi, there.

37:33.000 --> 37:34.916
We'll take a quick look
and then go.

37:35.000 --> 37:36.791
