37:51.083 --> 37:52.166
May I?

37:52.250 --> 37:53.375
Yes, yes, go ahead.

38:11.208 --> 38:12.333
Kitchen's fine.

38:12.416 --> 38:13.541
Where's the bathroom?

38:14.041 --> 38:15.833
The bathroom's right there.

38:21.000 --> 38:23.500
You know,
my son's crazy about comic books.

38:23.583 --> 38:26.208
