to the little woman you like?

45:39.875 --> 45:42.375
-What are you talking about?
-Don't play dumb.

45:42.458 --> 45:44.833
I saw her picture in the bathroom
behind the tranquilizers.

45:44.916 --> 45:47.166
I don't even wanna know
why you put it in there.

45:47.958 --> 45:49.416
So what's her name?

45:50.375 --> 45:51.375
Rebecca.

45:52.625 --> 45:55.375
And what about the friend who
was looking out with her from the landing?

45:55.458 --> 45:59.166
Well, she's from Seville.
