45:59.250 --> 46:01.208
They did a semester abroad together.

46:01.291 --> 46:02.625
The Spanish are beautiful.

46:02.708 --> 46:04.166
Clean, no makeup.

46:04.958 --> 46:06.291
All natural.

46:10.458 --> 46:13.875
-Have you ever spoken to Rebecca?
-No.

46:18.750 --> 46:19.833
Yes.

46:21.333 --> 46:24.458
Yes, we talked a few times
because she wanted to borrow my DVDs.

46:24.541 --> 46:28.166
