does he know about Nietzsche?"

47:40.708 --> 47:41.708
Well…

47:43.583 --> 47:47.208
Instead, I'm thinking it's
not gonna be easy to get out of here.

47:58.166 --> 47:59.000
Got it?

47:59.083 --> 48:00.791
